    <div class="section banner bg-video" id="banner">
     <div class="visually-hidden">
      <p>
       Description of the following video:
      </p>
      <p>
       We see animated text that first says “We will” next to the IU trident.
      </p>
      <p>
       Those words stay on the screen as other phrases take turns displaying to complete the sentence.
      </p>
      <p>
       The sentences displayed are:
      </p>
      <p>
       We will speak up.
      </p>
      <p>
       We will take action.
      </p>
      <p>
       We will embrace differences.
      </p>
      <p>
       We will make IU a better place.
      </p>
      <p>
       The animated text then replays continually on a loop.
      </p>
     </div>
     <div class="bg-image-cover" style="background-image: url('videos/we-will-still.jpg');">
     </div>
     <div class="bg-video-viewport" data-height="600" data-mp4="videos/we-will-5.mp4" data-webm="videos/we-will-5.webm" data-width="1800">
